With the release of his latest album, Billion Dollar Dream, a body of work chronicling his music journey, multi-talented artiste, Ani Jeremiah Chukwuebuka aka Jeriq has continued to soar in the Nigerian music scene. The album elbowed its way to number four, right behind Sarkodie’s No Pressure, Above Omar Sterling and O’Kenneth on Audiomack Ghana. In the UK, it snuck past Polo G, T. Dollar, M. Huncho and Eminem’s The Eminem show. Billion Dollar Dream album flourished and amassed millions of streams on the first week of its release. Almost two months after its release, it is still on Apple music’s top 20 albums.